WEBVTT

00:08:59.841 --> 00:09:04.496
it was never going to give those kids
what they really needed:

00:09:05.949 --> 00:09:07.449
their families.

00:09:09.298 --> 00:09:12.317
I know that it can feel
incredibly depressing

00:09:12.341 --> 00:09:16.096
to learn that helping vulnerable children
and overcoming poverty

00:09:16.120 --> 00:09:19.659
is not as simple as we've all
been led to believe it should be.

00:09:20.921 --> 00:09:23.943
But thankfully, there is a solution.

00:09:24.664 --> 00:09:28.462
These problems are reversible
and preventable,

00:09:28.486 --> 00:09:30.500
and when we know better,